profile ─┬─ automatic
         │  profiles applied automatically due to entries made
         │  in the Identity map files
         │
         ├─ driver
         │  profiles applied automatically due to the
         │  selected driver
         │
         ├─ manual
         │  profiles not applied automatically for manual
         │  use on the commandline or implicit via libsax
         │
         └─ script
            dynamic profile scripts bound to base profile
            which has to have the same base name. The dynamic
            part of a profile must be written in perl
